(2067, 581, 'Your Guide to the Best Beer Bars in the San Fernando Valley (East) - Hopped LA', '', 'http://localhost:8888/best-beer-bars-san-fernando-valley-east/', '206.130.117.200', '2014-09-12 10:42:23', '2014-09-12 17:42:23', '[&#8230;] Yup, it&#8217;s another bottle shop. But it&#8217;s not just any other bottle shop &#8211; it&#8217;s the giant of the east SFV where Green Jug is that of the west. Any trip to Valley Beverage Co. will ensure you don&#8217;t leave empty handed as their beer selection is fantastic. They are also one of the few places in town to grab bottles of the hard-to-find whales that grace the shelves in the back (meaning you need to ask for them). The downside is that EVERYBODY knows when the shipments come in, which means if you don&#8217;t get here fast then that beer you wanted&#8230;is already gone. Don&#8217;t worry, wait a few days until Vendome of Toluca Lake gets the same beer in and you&#8217;ll probably get your hands on it. Get our take on Vendome in our &#8220;#InsideTheBottleShop&#8221; series. [&#8230;]', 0, '1', 'The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library -- WordPress/3.9.2', 'pingback', 0, 0),
