(22935, 711, 'Sweeney&#039;s Ale House: The Best Place to Drink Craft Beer in Encino - Hopped LA', '', 'http://hoppedla.com/know-sweeneys-ale-house-encino/', '206.130.117.200', '2015-02-16 14:31:35', '2015-02-16 22:31:35', '[&#8230;] to a neighborhood of the San Fernando Valley that definitely needed it, bridging the gap between Sherman Oaks&#8217; restaurant row and the West [&#8230;]', 0, '1', '', 'pingback', 0, 0),
