(22975, 1942, 'Matthew Moran', 'matthewgmoran@gmail.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/smokin_ales/', '38.106.51.98', '2016-02-25 16:37:48', '2016-02-26 00:37:48', 'Hey Gary, I sincerely apologize. I did mix your post up with an, obviously, unreliable site and posted my comments on the wrong page...they have since updated yesterday. Father''s office (CC) did seem to be fielding a lot of inquiries yesterday. I did confirm they will be tweeting the day of, most likely 2-3 hours before they open.\n\nFeel free to delete my post or provide ten lashings in return. Thank you for all the info. Best.', 0, '1', '', '', 22972, 0),
(22976, 1942, 'Gary Magnone', 'gmagnone@gmail.com', 'http://www.hoppedla.com', '76.169.60.186', '2016-02-25 18:13:16', '2016-02-26 02:13:16', 'No worries man! It''s just awesome you cared enough to comment. We welcome any and all feedback. Hope you''ve gotten a pour of the Younger, or if not, hope you do soon. It''s tasting good this year. Cheers!', 0, '1', '', '', 22975, 4),
