(23, 1, '2014-04-08 15:00:16', '2014-04-08 22:00:16', 'It''s no surprise that craft beer in Southern California has been blowing up over the past few years. With a new brewery opening up what seems like every other month, it''s gotten a little tough to keep track of all the new local beer producers in Los Angeles, Orange County, and Ventura County.\r\n\r\nEnter Hopped LA''s Brewery Finder. Whether you''re looking to plan a weekend excursion, a local spot to fill a growler, or organizing a brewery tour for your birthday, the Brewery Finder will point you in the right direction. With currently 50 craft brewery locations listed across LA, OC &amp; Ventura, and a bunch more on the way, you can be sure to find an awesome beer spot near you!\r\n\r\nIf you find the Brewery Finder useful, don''t be selfish, share it with a friend! If you have any suggestions on how to make the Brewery Finder better, <a href="mailto:info@hoppedla.com?subject=Brewery%Finder%Update">drop us a line</a>. Cheers!\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #555555;">[put_wpgm id=1]\r\n<em>Last updated 11/24/14</em></span></p>', 'The Ultimate LA, OC & Ventura Craft Brewery Finder', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brewery-finder', '', '', '2014-11-24 21:37:25', '2014-11-25 05:37:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=23', 0, 'page', '', 0),
