(1113, 4, '2014-09-19 18:30:26', '2014-09-19 18:30:26', 'Melrose is one of the best examples of a west coast IPA out there. Full of Simcoe and Amarillo hops, it''s is perfectly balanced with a touch of Canadian honey to bring out the citrusy hop characteristics. Add a heavy dry-hop action, and you''ve got aroma for days.', 'Melrose - IPA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beachwood-bbq-brewing-melrose-ipa', '', '', '2016-02-23 14:47:09', '2016-02-23 22:47:09', '', 0, 'http://growler.progressionstudios.com/?post_type=beers&#038;p=96', 0, 'beers', '', 0),
(1114, 4, '2014-09-19 18:31:57', '2014-09-19 18:31:57', 'When guava and passionfruit collide in a tart, wild ale, only good things can happen. That''s what Highland Park Brewery experienced when they utilized their own fruit from the parking lot, and then aged 30% of the beer in red wine barrels and 70% in stainless steel. When it gets released again, don''t hesitate.', 'Raised Eyebrows - Wild Ale', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'highland-park-brewery-raised-eyebrows', '', '', '2016-02-23 14:37:10', '2016-02-23 22:37:10', '', 0, 'http://growler.progressionstudios.com/?post_type=beers&#038;p=103', 0, 'beers', '', 0),
(1115, 4, '2014-09-19 18:32:26', '2014-09-19 18:32:26', 'Mumford''s flagship black ale is super drinkable at 7.75% and has all the richness you''d expect from the dark malts. It''s definitely a beer to try from a brewery to pay attention to.', 'Black Mamba - Black Ale', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mumford-brewing-black-mamba', '', '', '2016-02-23 14:36:08', '2016-02-23 22:36:08', '', 0, 'http://growler.progressionstudios.com/?post_type=beers&#038;p=104', 0, 'beers', '', 0),
(1116, 4, '2014-09-19 18:32:53', '2014-09-19 18:32:53', 'In the world of tart sours brewed in LA, Cuddlebug might be the best. Or at least one of them. It''s release is bookmarked by any craft aficionado and is guaranteed to sell out. The wild ale is highlighted by peaches and apricots and is extremely sessionable at 4.5% ABV.', 'Cuddlebug - Wild Ale', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'smog-city-cuddlebug', '', '', '2016-02-23 14:31:58', '2016-02-23 22:31:58', '', 0, 'http://growler.progressionstudios.com/?post_type=beers&#038;p=105', 0, 'beers', '', 0),
(1117, 4, '2014-09-19 18:33:33', '2014-09-19 18:33:33', 'Coming in at a hot 10.5% ABV, the hops do a great job at balancing this big beer. With a myriad of flavors ranging from citrus, pine, and onion, it''s all supported nicely with a sweet vanilla backbone making this a solid triple IPA.', 'Power Plant - Triple IPA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'el-segundo-power-plant', '', '', '2016-02-23 13:44:48', '2016-02-23 21:44:48', '', 0, 'http://growler.progressionstudios.com/?post_type=beers&#038;p=106', 0, 'beers', '', 0),
